data.description: MLS# 269425 Don't miss out on this exceptional chance to transform this home into your dream haven. With a little love and attention, you can unlock its true potential and create a space that truly reflects your unique style. Welcome to the desirable neighborhood of Great West Richland, offering convenient access to schools, shopping, and major freeways. Nestled within this fantastic community, you'll find a spacious 2191 sqft home awaiting your creative vision. Fantastic Value: Priced to sell, this property presents a remarkable opportunity for buyers who are ready to roll up their sleeves and add their personal touch to make it shine. Endless Potential: Grab your hammer, paintbrush, and gloves as you envision the countless possibilities for this home. A few dent and ding projects, such as refreshing the carpets and adding a fresh coat of paint, will breathe new life into this space. Enjoy the luxury of a large backyard, with the lot stretching an impressive 199 feet deep. Imagine the possibilities for outdoor living and create your own oasis.  Take advantage of the proximity to parks within the neighborhood, providing abundant opportunities for recreation and creating cherished memories.  Ample Space: With 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and an open great room concept, this home offers plenty of room for comfortable living and entertaining.  Limited Showings: Please consult your trusted Realtor today to schedule a showing, as availability for viewings is limited. Don't miss out on this exceptional chance to transform this home into your dream haven. With a little love and attention, you can unlock its true potential and create a space that truly reflects your unique style. For further information or to schedule a viewing, please contact your Realtor without delay.
